properties.description: part of full name of person

properties.description: the subject has the object as their spouse (husband, wife, partner, etc.). Use "unmarried partner" (P451) for non-married companions

properties.label: languages spoken, written or signed
properties.description: language(s) that a person or a people speaks, writes or signs, including the native language(s)

properties.label: instance of

properties.description: notable scientific, artistic or literary work, or other work of significance among subject's works
